Dawn Rutledge
Executive Assistant
Dawn.Rutledge@horizonfs.com
As John’s “right hand,” Dawn prepares/processes new annuity applications and securities account paperwork and ensures that all accounts are properly funded.  Additionally, she can assist you with most service needs including fund transfers, withdrawals, reallocations, and distributions. Dawn is available to answer any questions you may have regarding your account or pending application.
Read More
Yvonne Albarran
Accounts Receivable Specialist/IT Solutions Coordinator
Yvonne.Albarran@horizonfs.com
Yvonne is a graduate of Broward Community College with an Associate degree in Business Administration.  In 1990, she began her career with Prudential Financial as a Senior Service Coordinator.  Although she enjoyed the path her career was following at that time, the birth of her first child led Yvonne to reassess her balance of career and family. She decided to become a stay-at-home mom.
